ne Arts, and a selection of beautiful reproductions of Van Horne's personal notebooks and exquisite watercolours from the archives of the Art Gallery of Ontario. Published in conjunction with a major exhibition at the Gardiner Museum in Toronto and the Montreal Museum of Fine Arts, Obsession presents a remarkable collection in the context of the life and career of a nineteenth-century Canadian business giant.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aPorcelain, JapanesevExhibitions. 0aPotteryzJapanvExhibitions. 0aPottery, JapanesexPrivate collectionszQuébec (Province)zMontréalvExhibitions. 0aPottery, JapanesexPrivate collectionszQuébec (Province)zMontréalvExhibitions. 7aART / Asian / General.2bisacsh1 aBondil, Nathalie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrooke, Janet M., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrowne, Kelvin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraham, Ron, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGraham, Ron, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aNewman, Peter C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTakesue, Akiko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVigo, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311127363108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2018z978311127598740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780773554764?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780773554764423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780773554764/original  a978-3-11-127363-1  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-127598-7